      <cell id="cwnzbjqpzbov4rlf">
        <desc><![CDATA[&lt;p&gt;This directly addresses the research insight that &lt;em&gt;&quot;the winning PN platform behaves like a tool, not a repository.&quot;&lt;/em&gt; Separating &lt;strong&gt;Complications&lt;/strong&gt; into its own top-level section is a deliberate differentiator — no competitor owns that space, and it was the #1 content gap named by stakeholders (triglyceride management, glycemic instability, pharmacy stability). This structure also aligns perfectly with the recommended content pillars from the findings deck (PN Fundamentals, Safety, Prescriptions, Complications, Evidence).&lt;/p&gt;]]></desc>
